v3
	* Additional documentation added to the script for clarity.

v2
	* The ability to round to the nearest tick is added.
	* The ability to change the weighting of the calculation is added.

v1
	* Standard intraday pivot calculations are made, based upon an amount
	of time in minutes, and plotted.
